(11,1,"2019-09-10 02:04:31","2019-09-10 02:04:31","<!-- wp:heading {\"className\":\"cursive font-large\"} -->\n<h2 class=\"cursive font-large\">You were made to do more than just function, you were made to flourish! </h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator {\"className\":\"is-style-wide\"} -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator is-style-wide\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3,\"align\":\"center\"} -->\n<h3 style=\"text-align:center\">Mission</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p> At Sound Heart Integrative Counseling I provide a safe non-judgmental space and listen to you deeply so that I can understand you as a whole person. I offer support in overcoming anxiety and depression, recovering from trauma and emotional injury, developing better relationships and interpersonal skills, obtaining greater self-knowledge, nurturing faith, and reconnecting with your Divine Nurturer. I provide this type of counseling support so that you can feel better, live a more meaningful life, and become a resilient and beautiful contributor to your family and society.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>I firmly believe the goal of counseling is not just to support people to cope with life, but to thrive and live a meaningful life!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":105} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"http://muslim-therapy.local/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/nuh-enes-sakalli-7QeqI5S2On8-unsplash-1-1024x576.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-105\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:quote -->\n<blockquote class=\"wp-block-quote\"><p>“You were born with wings, why prefer to crawl through life?”</p><cite>  ~ Rumi </cite></blockquote>\n<!-- /wp:quote -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>I work from the understanding that God is the sole Healer and Doer. My role is to provide support in your journey of doing the necessary heart work to open yourself up to Divine Healing and Transformation.</p>