(34,1,"2019-09-10 04:41:49","2019-09-10 04:41:49","<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>1) Q: What is counseling?</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><br> A: Counseling is…</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><br> 2) What is Islamic psychology?</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><br> A: Islamic psychology is</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><br> 3) Can I benefit from these services if I’m not Muslim?</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>A: Yes, absolutely. My theoretical orientation is rooted in Islamic psychology, which means my understanding of the human being comes from the Islamic tradition. I believe all people can benefit from what the Islamic tradition has to offer on matters related to the intellect, the heart, and the spirit; similar to the same way “mindfulness” from the Buddhist tradition has benefited people of all beliefs.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2>RATES</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"align\":\"left\"} -->\n<p style=\"text-align:left\"><br> Individual Counseling: The standard rate is $120 per hour. A sliding scale rate of $40-$120 is available for individuals who have financial need. Couples and Family Counseling: The standard rate is $150 per hour. A sliding scale rate of $60 - $150 is available for couples and families who have financial need.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><br>Group Counseling: $35.00 per hour, per person.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><br>Presentations: Please contact Raumene directly to discuss rates for the type of presentation you are looking for. I accept cash, check, or card. To make an appointment by card, please type in the amount below and click “Pay Now.” You will be directed to PayPal’s website where you can securely complete your payment.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><br> 4) Can I benefit from services if I’m not religious or spiritual?<br> A: Yes. I have experience using CBT, DBT, EMDR, emotionally focused, and other modalities and interventions to help all people feel better and reduce anxiety, depression, PTSD symptoms, relationship challenges, and more.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2>RESOURCES</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><br> -The Five Love Languages<br> -Seven Principles of Making Marriage work<br> -The Temperament God Gave You<br> -The Essential Enneagram<br> -Hakim Archuletta<br> -Agenda to Change Our Condition<br> -Purify Your Gaze</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->","FAQ","","inherit","closed","closed","","15-revision-v1","","","2019-09-10 04:41:49","2019-09-10 04:41:49","",15,"http://muslim-therapy.local/15-revision-v1/",0,"revision","",0),
