(103,1,"2019-09-11 04:52:21","2019-09-11 04:52:21","<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Raumene offers counseling services to individuals, couples, families, and groups. He also provides presentations on Islam, Islamic Psychology, and working with Muslim clients to counseling agencies, hospitals, schools, religious organizations, companies and other groups.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\n<h4>Individual Counseling: </h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Individual counseling offers a confidential, judgment free, and supportive professional relationship that aims to support you in your life’s journey. Counseling can be used to gain greater knowledge and awareness of yourself, embark on a healing journey, find meaningful and effective solutions to challenges, learn new therapeutic skills, and work towards achieving your life goals.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\n<h4>Pre-Marital and Marriage Counseling:</h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p> Pre-marital counseling offers a confidential supportive space for people who want to make sure they are a good match for each other and/or prepare for marriage. Marriage counseling supports married couples in resolving problems in their relationship and creating a deeper connection to each other. The</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>counselor supports couples in understanding one another more deeply through active<br> listening, reflection, learning about each another, and developing effective<br> communication skills. The counselor supports the couple in understanding each person’s<br> needs, temperament, communication style, and addresses barriers to achieving a healthy<br> and fulfilling relationship for both people.<br> =Family Counseling: Family counseling offers a confidential and supportive space for two<br> or more members of a family to resolve problems that arise in their relationship(s). The<br> counselor helps the family understand each family member, the dynamics of the family<br> system, explores expectations, discusses roles, and supports the family in developing a<br> healthy way of relating to each other.<br>=Group Counseling: Group counseling offers an opportunity to process issues related to a<br> particular topic or topics. Group counseling often supports the development of<br> interpersonal skills, facilitates social cohesion, and promotes beneficial sharing for<br> mutual growth.<br>=Presentations and Workshops: I offer presentations and workshops to help organizations<br> and groups of people learn more about Islam, Islamic psychology, and important matters<br> related to working with Muslim clients and patients.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->","Services","","inherit","closed","closed","","13-revision-v1","","","2019-09-11 04:52:21","2019-09-11 04:52:21","",13,"http://muslim-therapy.local/13-revision-v1/",0,"revision","",0),
(104,1,"2019-09-11 04:54:20","2019-09-11 04:54:20","<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Raumene offers counseling services to individuals, couples, families, and groups. He also provides presentations on Islam, Islamic Psychology, and working with Muslim clients to counseling agencies, hospitals, schools, religious organizations, companies and other groups.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\n<h4>Individual Counseling</h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Individual counseling offers a confidential, judgment free, and supportive professional relationship that aims to support you in your life’s journey. Counseling can be used to gain greater knowledge and awareness of yourself, embark on a healing journey, find meaningful and effective solutions to challenges, learn new therapeutic skills, and work towards achieving your life goals.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\n<h4>Pre-Marital and Marriage Counseling</h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p> Pre-marital counseling offers a confidential supportive space for people who want to make sure they are a good match for each other and/or prepare for marriage. Marriage counseling supports married couples in resolving problems in their relationship and creating a deeper connection to each other. The counselor supports couples in understanding one another more deeply through active listening, reflection, learning about each another, and developing effective communication skills. The counselor supports the couple in understanding each person’s needs, temperament, communication style, and addresses barriers to achieving a healthy and fulfilling relationship for both people.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\n<h4>Family Counseling</h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Family counseling offers a confidential and supportive space for two<br> or more members of a family to resolve problems that arise in their relationship(s). The counselor helps the family understand each family member, the dynamics of the family system, explores expectations, discusses roles, and supports the family in developing a healthy way of relating to each other.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\n<h4>Group Counseling </h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Group counseling offers an opportunity to process issues related to a<br> particular topic or topics. Group counseling often supports the development of interpersonal skills, facilitates social cohesion, and promotes beneficial sharing for mutual growth.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\n<h4>Presentations and Workshops</h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p> I offer presentations and workshops to help organizations and groups of people learn more about Islam, Islamic psychology, and important matters related to working with Muslim clients and patients.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->","Services","","inherit","closed","closed","","13-revision-v1","","","2019-09-11 04:54:20","2019-09-11 04:54:20","",13,"http://muslim-therapy.local/13-revision-v1/",0,"revision","",0),
